text: Hey @FedEx do you guys know any good luthiers in Atlanta who can fix what your guys did? https://t.co/nsZx8t5vfJ
@stillupsocut @FedEx It was packed about about as well as anything could be packed. They must’ve just abused it.

FWIW guitar buds - Don’t ship or insure with @FedEx. Some of you saw the pictures of the guitar that they damaged in shipping. They recently denied the insurance claim we put through. The claims process was murky and hard to navigate as well. Don’t waste your time or money.
@AliceinCovers @FedEx The whole process is designed to make you give up. Very clever of them honestly.
